readme:
# Base16 Roman Dark Syntax theme

Atom theme using the ever popular [Base16 Tomorrow](http://chriskempson.github.io/base16/#tomorrow) dark colors.

This theme has less agressive coloring compared to original [Base16 Tomorrow Dark Theme](https://atom.io/themes/base16-tomorrow-dark-theme)
